data.text:
Dis-Moi Oui Episode Summary Cast and Characters

“Dis-Moi Oui” is the third episode of Season 6. The episode was released on November 16, 2023.

Synopsis[]

Diana has another vacation with Dodi on the Fayed boat, but after returning to London, Diana starts to think about getting back together with William and Harry because Dodi is exhausted from a harsh lawsuit filed by his ex-fiancee.

Episode Notes[]

Historical Events[]

The deaths of Diana, Princess of Wales and Dodi Fayed

Historical Figures[]

Henri Paul: The car's driver during the high speed chase at Pont d'Alma in Paris that lead to Diana's death

Trevor Rees Jones: Diana's bodyguard and the only survivor of the 1997 crash

Historical Notes[]

Trivia[]

The opening scene from “Persona Non Grata” is used during the climax of the episode

The episode's title means "tell me yes" in French. It is also a reference to the engagement ring Dodi purchased for Diana.
